    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Make every hair care routine magical with the Officially Licensed Paddle Brush! Designed with soft, gentle bristles, this adorable brush easily detangles hair without pulling, making it perfect for little ones learning how to style and care for their hair. Gentle Detangling</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Girls Cartoon Paddle Detangling Hair Brush Minnie Mouse Barbie Lilo &amp; Stitch</h2>\n  <p>Make every hair care routine magical with the Officially Licensed Paddle Brush! Designed with soft, gentle bristles, this adorable brush easily detangles hair without pulling, making it perfect for little ones learning how to style and care for their hair.</p>\n  <p>Gentle Detangling</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>OFFICIALLY LICENSED PADDLE BRUSH - Barbie, Minnie Mouse or Lilo and Stitch brush options</li>\n    <li>GENTLE DETANGLING - Hair brush features soft bristles to gently detangle hair</li>\n    <li>LEARN HAIR CARE - Brush teaches little girls how to style and care for their hair</li>\n    <li>SAFE FOR KIDS - Paddle brush is safe for children ages 3 and up with supervision</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Officially licensed; Size:</strong> one size fits all; Material: plastic</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/toys/paddle_brush_parent.jpg\" alt=\"Make every hair care routine magical with the Officially Licensed Paddle Brush\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Multicolor</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Say goodbye to tears and tangles! The soft bristles smoothly glide through hair, providing a comfortable brushing experience for kids of all ages.</p>\n  <p>Learn Hair Care</p>\n  <p>This cute brush helps teach young girls how to care for and style their hair, making it a fun and educational part of their daily routine.</p>\n  <p>Safe &amp; Easy to Use</p>\n  <p>Safe for children ages 3 and up (with adult supervision), the paddle brush is the perfect size for small hands and is made from durable, lightweight plastic.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
